{"tid":2418421,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"城大新創普通話校歌   同學必須尊重校歌    勢成shitty 「郭安法」","createTime":"2021-02-22T15:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T02:05:41.000Z","uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca96cb743ee1b20168a715cf896bc0a80d673b6","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"香港城市大學今日（22號）舉行傳媒春茗，副校長（發展及對外關係）李國安表示，為加強大學定位及品牌，今年會推出新校歌，內容主要係鼓勵師生專心教學。校歌已經寫好普通話、廣東話版本，英文版就仲改緊。<br />\n<br />\n城大校長郭位表示，新校歌《學研出塵》代表佢對教學嘅看法，希望學校能做到政治中立，以教學為主。"},{"pid":"e72ec6ed40d0eb7d91802d7edd3b0749b9074be2","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:04:41.000Z","msg":"李國安話，留意到<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">唔少中小學都有校歌</span></span>，為咗令更多人了解城大，所以就構思創作新校歌。校歌將會由校長郭位填詞，希望師生能專心從事教學同研究工作。"},{"pid":"93292d21446749a59162645cf9924e6d6ed79538","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"被問到早前有城大學生將歌手李克勤嘅流行曲《畢業禮》填詞成《找郭位》，李國安就只係回應話：「任何人喺社會上做啲咩、講啲咩都要自行負責」。佢就只係會關注校歌嘅創作，管理學生行為嘅事就交畀其他部門處理。<br />\n<br />\n但呢首歌今日「發布會」上都仲未有得聽。城大話會喺聽日正式公布。目前有廣東話同普通話版本，而英文版仲係修改緊。<br />\n<br />\n城大喺舊年底增設「校歌法」「校徽法」等校規，禁止學生破壞大學品牌及形象包括惡搞校歌（例如《找郭位》）、校徽（例如將logo改成反檯「全部同我企起身」)嘅行為，被坊間恥笑為「郭安法」。<br />\n<br />\n《找郭位》一曲諷刺校長郭位喺城大被警察攻打時消聲匿跡，城大紀律委員會裁定涉事學生恐嚇或欺凌、迫害他人及傷害校譽，需罰寫道歉信畀郭位同校方，並禁足校園一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n另外，城大公關今次閉門春茗唔再廣邀記者，只係請咗10間傳媒，當中唔包括 《蘋果》、《立場》，亦都惹人非議。據聞本來公關應承傳媒有問答環節，但突然宣布時間唔夠而取消問答環節，惹起公憤。"},{"pid":"5b0e108b54e11f52cef0918e3188c0181c97435f","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgongjyuhok.hk%2Farticles%2F5373&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=5aaf0b4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gongjyuhok.hk/articles/5373</a><br />\n<br />\nshitty又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9aef6dc81bf3cf6ba3c67787034eb3937772c24","tid":2418421,"uid":204929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"改個名都衰過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 李<span class=\"red\">國安</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c412d3ca063f17ce43ca0b6d1b322508da9aebe","tid":2418421,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"吾shit又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d935f307413497fdb8dcd5a3f8be93cf0bae4b","tid":2418421,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"城市中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4622d12758613fc5cff076bc5b879753c3370d","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9aef6dc81bf3cf6ba3c67787034eb3937772c24","tid":2418421,"uid":204929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:07:09.000Z","msg":"改個名都衰過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 李<span class=\"red\">國安</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"人如其名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e9b0297539f82f903f563f06d95e3acef0ac9c","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2d935f307413497fdb8dcd5a3f8be93cf0bae4b","tid":2418421,"uid":71632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:12:42.000Z","msg":"城市中學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"城市小學<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37efd016bc00931e7eaf51aff454a00de2d7e8f","tid":2418421,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:01:34.000Z","msg":"其他幾間大學都有校歌<br />\n不過有無校歌對大學係咪咁大件事呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b235c0241664e42589034ba7ed3cb2971f30ac","tid":2418421,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c412d3ca063f17ce43ca0b6d1b322508da9aebe","tid":2418421,"uid":306109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"吾shit又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:01:39.000Z","msg":"城市小學屌打其他大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719c3069c1b51f2bd7e68e157df80c6067d8221e","tid":2418421,"uid":24311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a37efd016bc00931e7eaf51aff454a00de2d7e8f","tid":2418421,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:01:34.000Z","msg":"其他幾間大學都有校歌<br />\n不過有無校歌對大學係咪咁大件事呢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T02:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要將大學生當小學生咁教<br />\n歌頌愛國愛黨由校歌唱起"}]}